		- minor changes to spped up and adapt for new debugging tool
	-src/PrepareElectronSeed, PrepareMuonSeed (these tools should not be used any more):
		- minor changes to spped up and adapt for new debugging tool
		
	- options/TsaConfirmTool.opts: portation to Tf


